  <h3><a name="Lines_of_Communication"></a>Lines of Communication</h3>
  <p>I wish to efficiently answer your questions in a timely and efficient manner.  To direct your inquiry most efficiently please use the following guidelines:</p>
  <h4><a name="PERSON_TO_CONTACT"></a>PERSON TO CONTACT</h4>
    <h5><a name="Your_teacher"></a>Your teacher</h5>
  <p>While your child may occasionally receive occasional instruction from the parent (assistant teacher), your teacher functions as your primary provider of individual music assistance.  Communicate with him or her if you...</p>
  <ul>
    <li>... have questions about HOW or WHAT to practice at home</li>
